      <p class="- topic/p ">Accounting Considerations <ph class="- topic/ph ">
            <fn callout="2" id="UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6-aag-afi7-fn2" class="- topic/fn ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">For simplicity, this case study ignores income tax consequences.</p>
            </fn>
            <xref type="fn" class="- topic/xref " href="aag-afi7_accounting_considerations.dita#UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6_UUID-2b6edddb-334a-4b1a-9237-0e6ab8ff91a6/UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6-aag-afi7-fn2"/>
         </ph>
         <ph class="- topic/ph ">
            <fn callout="3" id="UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6-aag-afi7-fn3" class="- topic/fn ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph outputclass="shade grey" class="- topic/ph ">In April 2019, FASB issued ASU No.
                            2019-04, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Codification Improvements to Topic 326,
                                Financial Instruments — Credit Losses, Topic 815, Derivatives and
                                Hedging</i>, and <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Topic 825, Financial
                                Instruments</i> to clarify and improve areas of guidance
                            related to recently-issued ASU Nos. 2016-13, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Financial Instruments — Credit Losses (Topic 326): Measurement of
                                Credit Losses on Financial Instruments</i>, 2017-12,
                                <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Derivatives and Hedging (Topic 815):
                                Targeted Improvements to Accounting for Hedging
                                Activities</i>, and 2016-01, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Financial Instruments — Overall (Subtopic 825-10): Recognition and
                                Measurement of Financial Assets and Financial
                            Liabilities</i>. The ASU identifies the following five topic
                            categories:</ph>
               </p>
               <ul outputclass="ul bullet" class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph outputclass="shade grey" class="- topic/ph ">Topic 1: Codification
                                    Improvements Resulting from the June 11, 2018 and November 1,
                                    2018 Credit Losses Transition Resource Group (TRG)
                                    Meetings</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph outputclass="shade grey" class="- topic/ph ">Topic 2: Codification
                                    Improvements to Update 2016-13</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph outputclass="shade grey" class="- topic/ph ">Topic 3: Codification
                                    Improvements to Update 2017-12 and Other Hedging
                                    Items</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph outputclass="shade grey" class="- topic/ph ">Topic 4: Codification
