                                    TRG Meeting</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
               <p class="- topic/p ">Each topic category contains a variety of issues and the effective dates
                        for each issue depend on the topic category. “Pending Content” from Topic 1,
                        Issue 1B of the ASU is addressed in <xref format="dita" class="- topic/xref " href="../../../aag-afi/aag-afi7/aag-afi7_accounting_considerations/aag-afi7_accounting_considerations.dita#UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6_UUID-2b6edddb-334a-4b1a-9237-0e6ab8ff91a6/UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6_aag-afi7.05">paragraph 7.05</xref> of this guide. The amendments in Issue 1B are
                        effective as follows: for entities that have not yet adopted the amendments
                        in ASU No. 2016-13, the effective dates and transition requirements are the
                        same as those for that ASU; for entities that have adopted the amendments in
                        ASU No. 2016-13, the effective dates are for fiscal years beginning after
                        December 15, 2019, including interim periods within those fiscal years.
                        Early adoption is permitted. See the ASU, available at <xref scope="external" format="html" class="- topic/xref " href="https://fasb.org">fasb.org</xref>, for application
                        details.</p>
